EN: When dealing with issues, one should avoid rigidly sticking to their own position and should listen to the opinions of others.

ZH: 在快速发展的时代，人们务必要保持灵活应对，避免僵化。
EN: In this era of rapid development, people must remain flexible and avoid rigidity.

